1
00:01:28,880 --> 00:01:31,960
Zhenye, please don't be mad.

2
00:01:32,800 --> 00:01:34,759
You know our son.

3
00:01:35,240 --> 00:01:37,720
Jingxi is such an honest boy.

4
00:01:37,759 --> 00:01:38,890
Before the wedding,

5
00:01:39,280 --> 00:01:41,240
Zhixia was very close to him.

6
00:01:42,039 --> 00:01:43,700
He was afraid you'd blame him,

7
00:01:43,880 --> 00:01:45,400
and afraid of slighting Zhixia,

8
00:01:45,400 --> 00:01:47,259
so he never dared to say anything.

9
00:01:48,080 --> 00:01:50,720
Now everyone knows about this.

10
00:01:51,000 --> 00:01:53,729
Although it damaged the Lu family's reputation,

11
00:01:53,960 --> 00:01:56,280
we can't let the children suffer.

12
00:02:07,280 --> 00:02:08,240
Shen Zhixia.

13
00:02:09,560 --> 00:02:11,960
Since you are involved with Jingxi,

14
00:02:12,640 --> 00:02:14,640
why did you marry Jingheng?

15
00:02:15,960 --> 00:02:17,820
What do you take our Lu family for?

16
00:02:18,720 --> 00:02:19,760
Zhixia,

17
00:02:20,280 --> 00:02:21,880
Our Lu family

18
00:02:21,880 --> 00:02:23,740
is well-respected in our circle.

19
00:02:24,079 --> 00:02:27,040
Now that everyone knows about your scandals,

20
00:02:27,040 --> 00:02:28,900
how can our Lu family face anyone?

21
00:02:29,600 --> 00:02:30,520
Being well-respected

22
00:02:30,520 --> 00:02:33,600
doesn't stop someone from doing all kinds of bad things.

23
00:02:33,600 --> 00:02:35,280
There are two people in this photo.

24
00:02:35,280 --> 00:02:37,960
How did it become my fault alone?

25
00:02:43,320 --> 00:02:45,450
You're insulting me, sister-in-law.

26
00:02:47,400 --> 00:02:48,329
Sister-in-law.

27
00:02:48,880 --> 00:02:51,640
You were so close to me before the wedding.

28
00:02:52,440 --> 00:02:54,770
It breaks my heart to hear you say that now.

29
00:02:55,000 --> 00:02:56,560
As if I were the villain.

30
00:02:56,840 --> 00:02:57,680
Lu Jingxi.

31
00:02:58,079 --> 00:03:00,080
You are the only one who has this photo.

32
00:03:00,080 --> 00:03:01,880
If you didn't leak it on purpose,

33
00:03:01,880 --> 00:03:03,010
who else could it be?

34
00:03:03,480 --> 00:03:06,760
I wasn't the one who disgraced the Lu family.

35
00:03:07,440 --> 00:03:08,240
You did.

36
00:03:08,680 --> 00:03:11,140
Sister-in-law, that's a false accusation.

37
00:03:11,320 --> 00:03:13,040
Maybe you took a picture with your phone

38
00:03:13,040 --> 00:03:14,440
and sent it to someone to show off.

39
00:03:14,440 --> 00:03:15,160
Who knows?

40
00:03:15,920 --> 00:03:16,720
Shen Zhixia.

41
00:03:17,800 --> 00:03:19,600
No matter how ignorant my son is,

42
00:03:19,840 --> 00:03:22,900
he wouldn't dare joke with the Lu family's reputation.

43
00:03:23,440 --> 00:03:24,320
As for you,

44
00:03:25,000 --> 00:03:26,320
when others talk,

45
00:03:26,640 --> 00:03:29,640
they'll say the Lu family has an indecent daughter-in-law.

46
00:03:29,640 --> 00:03:31,480
Since you started this,

47
00:03:32,200 --> 00:03:34,840
you must give the Lu family an explanation.

48
00:03:34,880 --> 00:03:35,880
Her?

49
00:03:37,280 --> 00:03:39,410
What kind of explanation can she give?

50
00:03:39,680 --> 00:03:41,280
Our Lu family's loss,

51
00:03:41,400 --> 00:03:43,600
can your Shen family compensate for it?

52
00:03:43,680 --> 00:03:44,720
If you ask me,

53
00:03:44,960 --> 00:03:46,480
you should kneel down right now

54
00:03:46,480 --> 00:03:48,320
and apologize to everyone in our Lu family.

55
00:03:48,320 --> 00:03:49,120
Kneel down.

56
00:03:49,320 --> 00:03:50,160
Say that again.

57
00:03:50,160 --> 00:03:51,560
So what if I say it again?

58
00:03:51,560 --> 00:03:52,320
Enough.

59
00:04:20,800 --> 00:04:24,320
You resolve this yourselves.

60
00:04:25,400 --> 00:04:26,760
I want to see

61
00:04:27,560 --> 00:04:30,090
what kind of mess you can make of the Lu family.

62
00:04:34,400 --> 00:04:35,280
Shen Zhixia,

63
00:04:35,760 --> 00:04:37,320
look at what you've done.

64
00:04:38,000 --> 00:04:40,240
Your private life is a mess and you have no shame,

65
00:04:40,240 --> 00:04:41,840
yet you still act arrogant here.

66
00:04:41,840 --> 00:04:43,240
Now you've angered Uncle away.

67
00:04:43,240 --> 00:04:44,200
Are you satisfied?

68
00:04:44,200 --> 00:04:45,040
Miss.

69
00:04:46,280 --> 00:04:48,360
You can't say that about the Young Madam.

70
00:04:48,360 --> 00:04:50,680
The matter online hasn't been cleared up yet.

71
00:04:50,680 --> 00:04:53,080
You can't wrong her based on a single photo.

72
00:04:53,520 --> 00:04:54,320
Besides,

73
00:04:54,360 --> 00:04:56,290
the Young Master will be back soon.

74
00:04:56,520 --> 00:04:57,520
Once he returns,

75
00:04:57,520 --> 00:04:59,520
he will definitely find out the truth.

76
00:04:59,520 --> 00:05:01,120
Please don't make things difficult for her.

77
00:05:01,120 --> 00:05:02,380
In our family matters,

78
00:05:02,680 --> 00:05:04,640
since when do you have a say?

79
00:05:07,920 --> 00:05:08,720
Su Yuran,

80
00:05:08,880 --> 00:05:09,960
who do you think you are

81
00:05:09,960 --> 00:05:11,220
to look down on others?

82
00:05:11,480 --> 00:05:12,920
Let me tell you.

83
00:05:13,840 --> 00:05:14,920
As long as I'm here,

84
00:05:15,360 --> 00:05:16,720
no one can touch her.

85
00:05:18,280 --> 00:05:19,520
You forced me,

86
00:05:19,840 --> 00:05:22,040
just to make me leave the Lu family.

87
00:05:22,480 --> 00:05:24,240
I'm done playing this game.

88
00:05:24,560 --> 00:05:27,090
I'm taking Lili back to the Shen family today.

89
00:05:45,520 --> 00:05:47,280
Miss Shen, Miss Shen!

90
00:05:47,280 --> 00:05:48,200
It's rumored online that you cheated with your brother-in-law.

91
00:05:48,200 --> 00:05:49,040
Is it true?

92
00:05:49,040 --> 00:05:50,560
What's going on with the photo of you and the second young master of the Lu family?

93
00:05:50,560 --> 00:05:51,640
Can you give the public an explanation?

94
00:05:51,640 --> 00:05:52,760
The stock price of the Lu Group has plummeted.

95
00:05:52,760 --> 00:05:53,880
Is it because of your scandal?

96
00:05:53,880 --> 00:05:55,740
What does Mr. Lu think about this?

97
00:05:55,960 --> 00:05:56,690
Quan F·99999

98
00:05:56,720 --> 00:05:59,080
Mr. Lu.

99
00:06:00,920 --> 00:06:03,200
Mr. Lu.

100
00:06:03,200 --> 00:06:04,280
Please give an explanation, Mr. Lu.

101
00:06:04,280 --> 00:06:05,280
Mr. Lu,

102
00:06:05,280 --> 00:06:06,160
please give an explanation.

103
00:06:06,160 --> 00:06:08,000
Mr. Lu.

104
00:06:09,000 --> 00:06:11,040
What do you think of Miss Shen's scandal?

105
00:06:11,040 --> 00:06:13,600
Shen Zhixia is my lawfully wedded wife.

106
00:06:13,800 --> 00:06:14,930
I know her character

107
00:06:15,000 --> 00:06:16,400
better than anyone else.

108
00:06:17,040 --> 00:06:19,170
She doesn't need to explain to anyone.

109
00:06:21,400 --> 00:06:22,200
Let's go home.

110
00:06:23,280 --> 00:06:25,480
Mr. Lu.

111
00:06:25,480 --> 00:06:26,720
Please say a few more words.

112
00:06:26,720 --> 00:06:28,640
Mr. Lu.

113
00:06:28,640 --> 00:06:29,640
Just a few more words.

114
00:06:29,640 --> 00:06:30,880
Mr. Lu.

115
00:06:33,240 --> 00:06:34,480
Let go of me.

116
00:06:37,800 --> 00:06:39,240
If I hadn't rushed back just now,

117
00:06:39,240 --> 00:06:41,240
were you planning to just walk away?

118
00:06:41,840 --> 00:06:42,640
Lu Jingheng.

119
00:06:42,920 --> 00:06:45,040
My divorce can end this farce.

120
00:06:45,240 --> 00:06:46,040
Shen Zhixia.

121
00:06:46,400 --> 00:06:47,760
Do you know that this scandal

122
00:06:47,760 --> 00:06:50,000
caused Lu Group's stock to drop by three points?

123
00:06:50,000 --> 00:06:52,159
Besides, the cooperation between the Lu and Shen families

124
00:06:52,159 --> 00:06:53,520
hasn't been finalized yet.

125
00:06:53,520 --> 00:06:55,480
This marriage involves hundreds of millions in projects.

126
00:06:55,480 --> 00:06:58,140
You can't just get a divorce because you want to.

127
00:06:58,640 --> 00:07:00,360
That's your cooperation with Shen Jingyao.

128
00:07:00,360 --> 00:07:01,840
You can pursue it through the contract.

129
00:07:01,840 --> 00:07:03,240
Why can't I leave?

130
00:07:07,480 --> 00:07:09,520
Lu Jingheng, say something.

131
00:07:09,520 --> 00:07:10,920
Why can't I get a divorce?

132
00:07:30,480 --> 00:07:32,280
Mr. Lu.

133
00:07:33,320 --> 00:07:35,400
What do you think of Miss Shen's scandal?

134
00:07:35,400 --> 00:07:37,880
Shen Zhixia is my legally wedded wife.

135
00:07:38,120 --> 00:07:39,250
I know her character

136
00:07:39,320 --> 00:07:40,640
better than anyone.

137
00:07:41,360 --> 00:07:43,490
She doesn't need to explain to anyone.

138
00:07:44,680 --> 00:07:45,480
Let's go home.

139
00:07:49,240 --> 00:07:51,440
He's just acting for the Lu family.

140
00:07:51,720 --> 00:07:52,840
Wake up.

141
00:07:57,960 --> 00:07:58,800
Young Madam.

142
00:07:58,960 --> 00:07:59,760
Come in.

143
00:08:03,240 --> 00:08:03,840
Your milk.

144
00:08:03,840 --> 00:08:04,970
Just leave it there.

145
00:08:10,760 --> 00:08:12,320
Good thing there's no bruise.

146
00:08:12,320 --> 00:08:13,120
Hold this.

147
00:08:13,720 --> 00:08:16,180
Keep it on for a while to reduce the swelling.

148
00:08:22,960 --> 00:08:23,880
Silly.

149
00:08:24,120 --> 00:08:26,250
Why are you crying? You're a grown-up.

150
00:08:26,320 --> 00:08:27,240
Young Madam,

151
00:08:28,880 --> 00:08:30,040
since I was little,

152
00:08:30,640 --> 00:08:31,680
besides my mom,

153
00:08:32,280 --> 00:08:34,240
no one has protected me like you.

154
00:08:34,799 --> 00:08:38,000
Even if you really leave the Lu family,

155
00:08:38,440 --> 00:08:40,440
I'll follow you even to beg for food.

156
00:08:40,600 --> 00:08:42,000
Begging for food?

157
00:08:42,039 --> 00:08:44,320
Can't it be enjoying a good life?

158
00:08:45,640 --> 00:08:47,100
Yes, enjoying a good life.

159
00:08:47,400 --> 00:08:49,640
I'm blessed to be with you.

160
00:08:51,840 --> 00:08:53,040
Let me tell you,

161
00:08:53,280 --> 00:08:54,520
if it's still swollen,

162
00:08:54,520 --> 00:08:55,640
boil two eggs tomorrow

163
00:08:55,640 --> 00:08:57,360
and roll them on it to reduce swelling.

164
00:08:57,360 --> 00:08:57,880
Got it?

165
00:08:58,320 --> 00:08:59,440
By the way, Young Madam,

166
00:08:59,440 --> 00:09:01,040
Assistant Zhang told me today

167
00:09:01,040 --> 00:09:03,520
that the Young Master rushed back to protect you

168
00:09:03,520 --> 00:09:05,200
and hasn't eaten anything yet.

169
00:09:05,200 --> 00:09:06,930
And he has a stomach condition.

170
00:09:17,480 --> 00:09:18,810
What are you doing here?

171
00:09:20,120 --> 00:09:21,480
I heard you didn't eat.

172
00:09:21,480 --> 00:09:22,760
I cooked you some noodles.

173
00:09:22,760 --> 00:09:24,760
And brought some stomach medicine.

174
00:09:25,280 --> 00:09:27,280
The photo issue isn't resolved yet.

175
00:09:27,320 --> 00:09:28,560
And you still have the mood to cook?

176
00:09:28,560 --> 00:09:31,600
I don't know what happened before either.

177
00:09:31,600 --> 00:09:33,440
How can I explain it clearly?

178
00:09:34,480 --> 00:09:36,280
I can't explain the past.

179
00:09:36,360 --> 00:09:37,880
But just tell me now,

180
00:09:37,880 --> 00:09:39,640
how can I make up for the loss?

181
00:09:39,720 --> 00:09:41,000
I will cooperate fully.

182
00:09:41,000 --> 00:09:42,600
I just need one word from you.

183
00:09:44,000 --> 00:09:45,120
Do you still have Lu Jingxi in your heart?

184
00:09:45,120 --> 00:09:45,800
How is that possible?

185
00:09:45,800 --> 00:09:46,760
If the Lu family must choose one,

186
00:09:46,760 --> 00:09:48,420
I would definitely choose...

187
00:09:54,040 --> 00:09:56,000
I was just making an analogy.

188
00:09:56,360 --> 00:09:57,200
An analogy.

189
00:09:57,720 --> 00:09:58,600
I know.

190
00:10:24,640 --> 00:10:25,360
Miss.

191
00:10:25,360 --> 00:10:26,400
The master ordered that

192
00:10:26,400 --> 00:10:28,040
the annex is for your use from now on.

193
00:10:28,040 --> 00:10:29,480
The things you brought back from abroad

194
00:10:29,480 --> 00:10:31,680
have been moved to the second-floor bedroom.

195
00:10:31,680 --> 00:10:32,400
Got it.

196
00:10:55,280 --> 00:10:56,040
Jingheng.

197
00:11:00,480 --> 00:11:01,760
When I saw the trending searches,

198
00:11:01,760 --> 00:11:03,490
I was waiting for you to call me.

199
00:11:03,760 --> 00:11:05,160
After thinking about it,

200
00:11:05,160 --> 00:11:06,760
the crisis public relations

201
00:11:06,920 --> 00:11:08,320
still have to bother you.

202
00:11:08,640 --> 00:11:10,000
Zhuoyue is best at this.

203
00:11:10,600 --> 00:11:11,640
I'll prepare a bit.

204
00:11:11,640 --> 00:11:12,760
Let's talk in detail later.

205
00:11:12,760 --> 00:11:14,620
It concerns my wife, Shen Zhixia.

206
00:11:15,280 --> 00:11:16,480
If there are any details

207
00:11:16,480 --> 00:11:18,480
or anywhere she needs to cooperate,

208
00:11:18,760 --> 00:11:20,480
you really do need to talk in person.

209
00:11:20,480 --> 00:11:21,280
Perfect.

210
00:11:21,720 --> 00:11:23,520
I also want to meet Mrs. Lu.

211
00:11:24,720 --> 00:11:26,440
Your wedding was such a big event,

212
00:11:26,440 --> 00:11:28,360
I couldn't even be there to congratulate you.

213
00:11:28,360 --> 00:11:29,290
It's such a pity.

214
00:11:29,920 --> 00:11:31,320
See you in the afternoon.

215
00:11:56,040 --> 00:11:56,840
Mrs. Zhang.

216
00:11:56,840 --> 00:11:57,840
Why so enthusiastic today?

217
00:11:57,840 --> 00:11:59,240
Who are we hosting?

218
00:12:00,040 --> 00:12:01,800
The young master is upset about the scandal.

219
00:12:01,800 --> 00:12:02,660
But look at you,

220
00:12:02,720 --> 00:12:03,840
acting like nothing happened.

221
00:12:03,840 --> 00:12:05,640
What kind of wife acts like this?

222
00:12:06,600 --> 00:12:07,400
Wait a minute.

223
00:12:07,720 --> 00:12:10,280
Who exactly is coming today?

224
00:12:10,280 --> 00:12:12,400
Young Madam, Miss Wen is coming.

225
00:12:12,400 --> 00:12:14,320
The Wen and Lu families are old friends.

226
00:12:14,320 --> 00:12:16,400
She's been visiting since she was little.

227
00:12:16,400 --> 00:12:19,060
The young master went to the door to welcome her.

228
00:12:20,640 --> 00:12:21,480
Miss Wen?

229
00:12:22,800 --> 00:12:24,800
Went personally?

230
00:12:48,720 --> 00:12:49,720
This is my friend,

231
00:12:49,840 --> 00:12:51,200
Miss Wen Shuyi.

232
00:12:51,680 --> 00:12:53,600
She is very experienced in PR.

233
00:12:53,760 --> 00:12:55,520
I specifically invited her

234
00:12:55,680 --> 00:12:58,080
to help solve your public relations crisis.

235
00:12:58,080 --> 00:12:58,680
This is...

236
00:12:58,680 --> 00:13:00,680
Hello, Mrs. Lu.

237
00:13:02,920 --> 00:13:04,320
Miss Wen is so beautiful.

238
00:13:04,440 --> 00:13:05,840
Nice to meet you.

239
00:13:08,720 --> 00:13:10,120
What a "nice to meet you".

240
00:13:10,480 --> 00:13:11,280
Shen Zhixia,

241
00:13:11,920 --> 00:13:14,000
