242
00:13:14,000 --> 00:13:16,440
Do you really think the past is over?

243
00:13:18,720 --> 00:13:20,380
You are too polite, Miss Shen.

244
00:13:22,120 --> 00:13:22,920
Jingheng,

245
00:13:23,200 --> 00:13:24,480
Regarding the PR plan,

246
00:13:24,480 --> 00:13:26,680
I want to talk to you in private about some details.

247
00:13:26,680 --> 00:13:27,480
After you.

248
00:13:44,040 --> 00:13:44,920
Young Master.

249
00:13:45,280 --> 00:13:46,080
Miss Wen.

250
00:13:46,600 --> 00:13:47,400
It's been so many years.

251
00:13:47,400 --> 00:13:49,200
You are still as elegant as ever.

252
00:13:49,200 --> 00:13:51,360
This is the almond cake you used to love.

253
00:13:51,360 --> 00:13:53,280
I had the kitchen prepare it early this morning.

254
00:13:53,280 --> 00:13:54,280
It's still hot.

255
00:13:54,840 --> 00:13:55,840
Thank you, Mrs. Zhang.

256
00:13:55,840 --> 00:13:58,560
Thank you for remembering my preferences after all these years.

257
00:13:58,560 --> 00:13:59,520
It's not just me.

258
00:13:59,520 --> 00:14:01,200
The long-time servants of the Lu family

259
00:14:01,200 --> 00:14:02,800
all miss Miss Wen.

260
00:14:03,520 --> 00:14:04,360
How about this?

261
00:14:04,360 --> 00:14:06,690
Let's go to the study and talk while we eat.

262
00:14:08,480 --> 00:14:09,360
Thank you, Mrs. Zhang.

263
00:14:09,360 --> 00:14:10,160
You're welcome.

264
00:14:10,160 --> 00:14:10,800
After you.

265
00:14:13,440 --> 00:14:15,520
Childhood sweethearts.

266
00:14:19,240 --> 00:14:20,880
Don't be angry.

267
00:14:21,840 --> 00:14:23,640
I'm not even from this world.

268
00:14:23,640 --> 00:14:25,300
What does it have to do with me?

